      <title>博客开启评论功能</title>
      <link href="/2024/10/23/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AF%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/"/>
      <url>/2024/10/23/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AF%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>此方法使用utterances插件，适用于任意主题,评论需要登录Github账号。<br>二编：[Meow]主题的作者更新了评论模块，使用了另一个系统giscus，所以这个网站的评论功能以后会改用giscus。但是对于没有评论模块的主题，这篇文章所写的方法依旧有用。</p><span id="more"></span><p>根据这篇文章的方法生成的评论区效果：<br><img src="/2024/10/23/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AF%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/Comment.png" alt="图片"><br>插件官网<a href="https://utteranc.es/">点击链接开启</a></p><h2 id="配置Github仓库"><a href="#配置Github仓库" class="headerlink" title="配置Github仓库"></a>配置Github仓库</h2><p>我们需要一个仓库储存评论。打开github,创建一个新的repositories<br><img src="/2024/10/23/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AF%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/1.png" alt="图片"><br><img src="/2024/10/23/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AF%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/2.png" alt="图片"></p><h2 id="安装GitHub-Apps-utterances"><a href="#安装GitHub-Apps-utterances" class="headerlink" title="安装GitHub Apps - utterances"></a>安装GitHub Apps - utterances</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/apps/utterances">安装链接</a><br>点击Install</p><p><img src="/2024/10/23/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AF%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/3.png" alt="图片"></p><p>选择刚刚创建的仓库</p><p><img src="/2024/10/23/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AF%E8%AF%84%E8%AE%BA%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD/4.png" alt="图片"></p><h2 id="在博客中使用"><a href="#在博客中使用" class="headerlink" title="在博客中使用"></a>在博客中使用</h2><p>最简单的方法：<br>在需要评论区的<code>博文.md</code>文件最后加入这段代码</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script src=&quot;https://utteranc.es/client.js&quot;</span><br><span class="line">repo=358603545/blog-comment</span><br><span class="line">issue-term=&quot;pathname&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  theme=&quot;github-light&quot;</span><br><span class="line">crossorigin=&quot;anonymous&quot;</span><br><span class="line">async&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>于是你就可以在文章的最后获得一个评论区<br>如果想要更美观也可以在代码前面加入<code>---</code>创建分割线</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">&lt;script src=&quot;https://utteranc.es/client.js&quot;</span><br><span class="line">repo=358603545/blog-comment</span><br><span class="line">issue-term=&quot;pathname&quot;</span><br><span class="line">  theme=&quot;github-light&quot;</span><br><span class="line">crossorigin=&quot;anonymous&quot;</span><br><span class="line">async&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
